{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe9e1b67d1","title":"毛泽东对中央关于揭露胡风反革命集团的指示稿的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"efb23e7693","index":0,"year":1955,"month":6,"day":3,"articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"af3a5210a3","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对中央关于揭露胡风反革命集团的指示稿的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"},{"id":"8cd7761e96","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"},{"id":"a0df73be96","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、邓小平、彭真阅后即发。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"},{"id":"ebc83279da","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东六月三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"},{"id":"ba44782b07","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"},{"id":"8a80c90d20","type":"paragraph","text":"各省市委和党组必须认识这一斗争的目的，不但在于肃清胡风反革命集团分子，主要地是借着这一斗争提高广大群众(主要是知识分子和干部)的觉悟，揭露各种暗藏的反革命分子(国民党特务分子，帝国主义的特务分子，托派分子和其他反动分子)，进一步纯洁革命队伍。因此，当斗争有了进一步的发展时，就要公开号召一切暗藏的反革命分子和反动分子进行自我坦白，这种坦白，向小组会向大会向负责人去做或写书面材料都可以。但在中学学生和小学学生中不要去进行这种坦白的号召。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1"}],"page":{"id":"c58c6a5c77","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fe9e1b67d1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}